<HEADLINE>
<P>
NORTH'S TRIAL IN IRAN-CONTRA FIASCO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
North is on trial because he twisted and warped what it means to be an 
American. Being born and raised in the United States, I was taught that we 
Americans believe in the individual, making our own choices, and standing on 
our own two feet. 
</P>
<P>
According to North, being a "good American" means taking orders with an 
enthusiastic, "Yes, sir!" No questions asked. As for myself, I thought people 
are supposed to do that under the rule of dictators and tyrants. 
</P>
<P>
VALERIE LOH 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
