TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; 
PALESTINIANS -- ISRAEL; BUSH, GEORGE; ISRAEL -- ELECTIONS; SELF REPRESENTATION; 
WEST BANK (ISRAEL); GAZA STRIP 
</P>
