2 BROTHERS BEHEADED AFTER 19 YEARS IN JAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
RIYADH, Saudi Arabia 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Two brothers convicted of murder have been beheaded in Saudi Arabia after 
spending the past 19 years in jail, local newspapers reported Friday. 
</P>
<P>
The brothers were jailed until the son of the man they killed came of age to 
decide if he wanted compensation or execution under the strict rules of Sharia 
(Islamic law). 
