SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST: COUNTYWIDE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Twenty San Diego County elementary schools were among 231 statewide named 
California Distinguished Schools for the 1988-89 school year, state schools 
Supt. Bill Honig announced Friday. 
</P>
<P>
