Julian School; Monterey Heights School in Lemon Grove; Pacifica and South 
Oceanside schools in Oceanside; Burbank, Fremont, Juarez and Spreckels 
elementaries in San Diego; Cajon Park, Carlton Hills and Chet F. Harritt 
schools in Santee, and Central, Imperial Beach, Nestor, Nicoloff, Sunnyslope 
and West View schools in South Bay. 
