NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
USC freshman sprinter Quincy Watts won the 200 meters in 20.82 seconds on the 
first day of competition in the USC Twilight track and field meet at Cromwell 
Field. 
</P>
<P>
Other Trojan winnners included Greg Harper, 52 feet 5 1/4 inches in the triple 
