NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Michel Bergeron, after two seasons with the New York Rangers, was named coach 
of the Quebec Nordiques, the team he led from 1980-87. 
</P>
<P>
He replaces Jean Perron, who resigned but will remain with the team as a scout. 
</P>
