-- Joel Manion of Saddleback shot a two-under 70 and teammate Bob Jacobson shot 
par 72 for Saddleback at Rancho San Joaquin golf course in Irvine. Rich Clifton 
of Golden West shot 72, and Tom Woliver of San Diego Mesa, Dan Yury and Chris 
Jacques of Fullerton all shot 73. 
